1
00:00:02,130 --> 00:00:03,500
-Okay,Chandler. -Okay.
-钱德 -好

2
00:00:03,700 --> 00:00:05,500
And your horoscope says:
你的星座运势说：

3
00:00:05,700 --> 00:00:09,160
