为什么？

8
00:00:20,950 --> 00:00:25,650
Wait. "On the 19th, a secret crush announces itself."
19日有人会向你表白

9
00:00:31,490 --> 00:00:32,620
-Hey,guys. -Hey.
大家好

10
00:00:32,830 --> 00:00:36,130
It's Joey Tribbiani of Mac and C.H.E.E.S.E.
天哪，是“麦克与吉事”的 乔伊崔比亚尼

11
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:40,030
That's right. It's your first day.
也对，你今天开拍

12
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:43,470
Are you psyched to fight crime with your robot sidekick?
高不高兴要和机器人拍档 打击假犯罪？

13
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:46,300
Am I? The lead in my own TV series?
我高不高兴有自己的影集？ 

14
00:00:46,510 --> 00:00:49,100
I've dreamed about this for years!
我梦想好多年了

15
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:51,340
