And that's only because it's there when you turn it on.
那还是因为那是首页

20
00:01:08,030 --> 00:01:10,930
Our spat will start early this month.
我们本月份的口角会提前发生 

21
00:01:11,130 --> 00:01:12,460
I'll be waiting.
我等你

22
00:01:14,570 --> 00:01:16,230
The One Where Ross Meets Elizabeth's Dad
本集播出：“拜见父亲大人”

00:01:17,570 --> 00:01:18,230
rainystar压制iPod-MP4

23
00:01:54,210 --> 00:01:58,670
Are you judging them by their covers? You're really not supposed to.
你看封面选书？这样不对喔

24
