00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,760
It was the guy who controls the robot.
不是机器人，是操作它的人 

180
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:10,420
He hates me. He had C.H.E.E.S.E. knock over the sandwich table...
他不喜欢我 我正要拿三明治 

181
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:12,720
right when I was reaching for one.
他就让吉事打翻盘子

182
00:11:12,930 --> 00:11:14,590
Why don't you get him fired?
你怎么不让他走路？

183
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:18,330
