00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:32,410
Joe! I'm glad I found you! I got an audition for you.
小子，找到你就好，有试镜

188
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:35,680
But it's kind of on the q.t.
这件事是个秘密

189
00:11:35,890 --> 00:11:39,590
The actor who has the part doesn't know he might be fired.
那个演员不知道 他可能会被换掉

190
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:41,820
It's the lead in a series.
是一部影集的主角 

191
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:43,550
Mac and C.H.E.E.S.E.
“麦克与吉事”

192
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:48,230
I'm the lead in Mac and C.H.E.E.S.E.
我就是“麦克与吉事”的主角

193
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,310
Joey?
乔伊？

194
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,170
Hi,Ross.
罗斯

195
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:02,850
I was just getting him to like you.
我在让他喜欢你

196
