Joey!
乔伊！

198
00:12:11,730 --> 00:12:13,420
Ross,Joey is not here.
罗斯，乔伊不在

199
00:12:13,690 --> 00:12:15,720
I'll just wait for him in here!
好，那我在房里面等

200
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,620
Ross,it's okay. You can come out.
罗斯，没关系，你可以出来

201
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,730
Yeah. It's okay. It's me...
没错，没关系，是我 

202
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:23,330
Mr. Stevens.
史提芬斯先生

203
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:28,200
I didn't... Oh,my gosh. I didn't even see you.
天哪，我刚才没看见你

204
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:32,000
You did. You came in, got all awkward and ran to the bedroom.
当然有，你走进来，觉得很窘

205
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:33,910
You were shouting,"Joey!"
就跑进房里去 还大叫“乔伊，乔伊”

206
00:12:36,580 --> 00:12:37,950
-Bye,Rachel. -Bye.
再见

207
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,140
I'll call you later.
我再打给你

208
00:12:39,420 --> 00:12:40,910
-See you. -Bye,Ross.
好，再见 罗斯再见

209
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:47,590
What? What the..? How did...? What?
你在…你怎么…你在怎么？

210
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:53,270
You know, he lost his keys. So he was looking for them.
他的钥匙掉了，就回来找

211
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:54,960
In your mouth?
在你的嘴里找？

212
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,470
No!
不是

213
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:00,700
Downstairs. And we got to talking...
在楼下找 我们聊了...

214
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:04,900
for two hours. I liked him. I invited him for coffee.
两小时，我很喜欢他 就请他上来喝杯咖啡

216
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:07,940
You were at the coffeehouse!
你们就在咖啡馆里

217
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:12,180
What's the big deal? So I kissed the guy.
就算我亲了他又怎样？

218
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:15,950
He is my girlfriend's father. It's weird!
他是我的女朋友的爸爸 这样很怪

219
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:19,620
-You dated my sister! -That was different!
你还不是跟我妹约会 那不一样

220
00:13:20,130 --> 00:13:23,790
-What? Why? -This is weird for me!
为什么？ 这次是我觉得怪

221
00:13:25,530 --> 00:13:27,760
Ross,look. This is good for you.
罗斯，这样对你有好处

222
00:13:28,340 --> 00:13:31,330
Let's face it. So far the guy's not loving you.
承认吧 目前他一点也不喜欢你

223
00:13:31,510 --> 00:13:35,000
