00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:04,530
Thanks. But I have a problem to deal with.
谢了，但我有问题要解决

233
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:08,170
No,you've got to win over the guy who controls C.H.E.E.S.E.
你得让那个操作员喜欢你

234
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:12,140
Go back there and kiss some serious robot ass!
你得用力拍他的机器马屁

235
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,740
That's not a bad idea!
这个主意不错

236
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:20,110
If I have to be charming tomorrow, I'm not wasting it on you guys.
既然明天要施展魅力 现在还是别浪费的好

237
00:14:20,290 --> 00:14:22,690
I got some saved for you, Phoebe.
不过菲比，我为你留了一点

238
00:14:26,930 --> 00:14:29,290
Do you think Joey is more charming than me?
你觉得乔伊比我有魅力？

239
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:32,030
Yeah. That's why I'm sleeping with him on the side.
对，所以我跟他有一腿

240
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:34,030
You wish.
你想得美喔

241
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:39,500
"You wish."
“你想得美喔”

242
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,100
Stop writing about us.
菲比，别再写我们了 

243
00:14:41,310 --> 00:14:44,610
I'm not writing about you. I'm writing about other people.
我没有，我是在写别人

244
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:48,810
-Who? -Marsha and Chester.
谁？ 摩莎和钱特

245
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:53,980
Fine. Then you know what? I will just write about Phyllis.
好，那我就来写菲莉丝

246
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:58,590
-"Phyllis is sitting in the chair." -I see what you're doing.
-菲莉丝坐在椅子上 -我知道你想干嘛

247
00:14:58,990 --> 00:15:01,430
"Phyllis sees what I'm doing."
菲莉丝知道我想干嘛

249
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:06,970
I have tasted my own medicine and it is bitter!
哇，我终于自食恶果了

250
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:14,230
Morning!
早

251
00:15:14,810 --> 00:15:17,330
How's my favorite genius and his robot?
我最欣赏的天才 和我的机器人兄弟好吗？

252
00:15:17,540 --> 00:15:19,670
-Don't touch him! -Okay.
别碰他 好

253
00:15:21,650 --> 00:15:25,880
Level with me. I keep hearing rumors that I might get fired.
韦恩，你老实说 我一直听说我会被换掉

255
00:15:26,190 --> 00:15:29,210
They even have actors reading for my part.
他们还找人来试我这个角色

256
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:32,150
Come on. You gotta give me a second chance.
拜托啦，再给我一次机会

257
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:34,020
I love this little guy.
我爱死这个小砘铩

258
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:39,030
That's why you didn't want me to touch him,right?
难怪你不让我碰他，拿去吧

259
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:45,000
I can't believe it. God!
白痴，真是的

260
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:48,870
Hey,how are you doing?
你好吗？

261
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:57,080
So it seemed that my prom date had stood me up.
看样子我是被放鸽子了 

262
00:15:57,450 --> 00:16:01,950
So Ross selflessly offered to take me.
罗斯就大方的提议要带我去

263
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:04,320
What a nice story.
好感人喔

264
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:06,150
So Ross was in college...
罗斯上大学时...

265
00:16:06,330 --> 00:16:10,990
and decided to jump at the chance to take a young girl to her prom.
想趁虚而入 带一名少女参加高中舞会

266
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:16,330
I definitely did not see that one backfiring.
想不到会有这种反效果

267
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:20,260
-I'm going to the bathroom. -Take your time.
我去洗手间 你慢慢上

268
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:26,780
I was a freshman and she was a senior. So it wasn't as bad as..
其实我是大一，她是高三 所以没那么…

269
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:29,980
Look. I know I've been giving you a lot of jabs.
罗斯，我知道我一直找你麻烦

270
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:34,380
It's partly because I'm very protective of Lizzie...
因为我很保护丽莎

271
00:16:34,990 --> 00:16:40,050
and partly because they just keep coming to me.
而且你的缺点实在很多

272
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:45,160
I admit after all the wonderful things Lizzie told me...
但是丽莎一直夸你 

273
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:50,600
and the many,many,many stories that Rachel has told me...
瑞秋又说了那么多事

274
00:16:51,470 --> 00:16:52,630
well...
看来...

275
00:16:54,110 --> 00:16:55,770
you're not...
你也…

276
00:16:56,610 --> 00:16:58,740
all bad.
没那么糟

277
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,470
"Not all bad."
是没那么糟

278
00:17:02,450 --> 00:17:05,680
I'm sorry I was so harsh. But you have to understand.
很抱歉之前对你那么凶 你必须知道

279
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:09,810
I still look at Lizzie like she's a 12-year-old girl.
丽莎在我眼中仍是个小女孩

280
00:17:10,320 --> 00:17:14,020
I know what you mean. I do that too.
我懂你的意思，我也有同感

281
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:20,160
-I beg your pardon? -I don't see her as a 12-year-old.
你说什么？ 不…我不是把她当成小女孩

283
00:17:20,900 --> 00:17:24,890
I mean,I have a son who is 6 and I still think of him as a baby.
我是说我有个6岁的儿子 在我眼中仍是个小宝宝

284
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:29,870
-A son? -My ex-wife and I share custody of Ben.
-你有儿子？ -对，我和前妻取得共同监护权

285
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,380
Incidentally,Carol and I are on excellent terms...
还有，卡萝和我的关系很好 

286
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:35,780
as I'm sure you are with your wife.
相信你和你太太也是

287
00:17:36,050 --> 00:17:38,080
I'm sorry.
抱歉

288
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:40,020
It's unbelievable!
我真是猪

289
00:17:40,850 --> 00:17:43,550
Don't worry. I didn't realize you were married.
没事，我只是不知道你结过婚

290
00:17:44,090 --> 00:17:47,460
We were. But that was just a...
我们是结过婚，那只是…

291
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:53,660
That was just a big drunken mistake.
那只是酒后闹事

292
00:17:56,300 --> 00:17:57,530
You're back.
你回来了

293
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,400
You two were married?
你们结过婚？

294
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:05,900
I'm sorry. You were talking about Emily.
抱歉，你在讲艾蜜莉

295
00:18:08,180 --> 00:18:11,410
We said we would meet at the coffeehouse at 6:00.
钱德，我们是约6点楼下见

296
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,640
We said 7:00.
我们是约7点 

297
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:14,390
We said 6:00!
我们是约6点

298
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:16,450
The only way that I said 6:00...
我如果有讲到6点 

299
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:21,420
would be if I said the sentence, "Let's meet at 7:00,not at 6:00."
应该是说：我们约7点 不要约6点

301
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:24,860
If I had said 7:00,I would have said:
我如果有讲到7点，应该是说

302
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:28,690
"My boyfriend is such a wiseass. 7:00!"
“我男朋友真自作聪明” “什么7点”

303
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:31,900
-Hi! -Oh,my good God!
天哪

304
00:18:32,670 --> 00:18:34,770
-I know what time you said. -What?
我知道你们约几点 什么？

305
00:18:35,210 --> 00:18:38,610
Well,I know what time Chester and Marsha said.
我知道摩莎和钱特约几点

306
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,570
What time?
几点？

307
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,810
Interesting turn of events.
真有趣的转变 

308
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:46,450
Suddenly it's my book to the rescue. Let's see.
我的书突然成了救星

309
00:18:47,690 --> 00:18:49,050
Very interesting.
有意思

310
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:52,220
Well this certainly clears things up.
这样就很清楚了

311
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,050
What does it say?
到底是几点？

312
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:58,520
I will tell you as soon as you thank me for writing my book.
你们谢谢我写书，我就说

313
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:02,520
Thank you for writing your book. It's a great book...
谢谢你写书  这真是一本好书 
 
314
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:05,370
and you are the queen of everything.
你是女王中的女王

315
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,670
Thanks. So are you.
谢谢，你也是

316
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:17,980
I told you I should not wear this color.
我就说我不该穿这个颜色

317
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:26,250
"Monica.. Marsha and Chester are planning on seeing a movie Sunday.
摩…摩莎和钱特 打算星期天晚上去看电影

318
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:31,430
"Marsha thinks they're meeting at 6:00. Chester thinks it's 7:00."
摩莎觉得应该约6点 钱特觉得电影是7点

319
00:19:32,170 --> 00:19:35,190
-You knew we were gonna miss the movie? -Right.
你知道我们会赶不上电影？ 没错

320
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:40,100
Instead of telling us, you decided to write it in your stupid book?
而你只把它写下来 不告诉我们？

321
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:42,800
"Marsha and Chester are mad at Phyllis."
摩莎和钱特很气菲莉丝

322
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:50,680
I can't believe I'm gonna lose this job.
我居然要被换角

323
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:53,450
I'm so sorry,man. Is there anything I can do?
真可惜，我能帮什么忙吗？

324
00:19:53,990 --> 00:19:58,120
Help me get this mini-fridge past the security guard.
能，帮我把那个小冰箱搬走

325
00:20:02,930 --> 00:20:05,020
Joey,I want to talk to you.
乔伊，我有事找你

326
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,700
I don't want to talk to you.
我可不想理你

327
00:20:07,870 --> 00:20:10,500
I hate you. You ruined my life.
我恨你，你毁了我的一生

328
00:20:10,670 --> 00:20:13,700
-Chandler,Wayne. Wayne,Chandler. -Hi.
钱德，韦恩，韦恩，钱德

329
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:16,930
I'll get you your job back if you help me out.
乔伊，你帮我 我就叫他们不要换角

330
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:19,240
Why should I help you out?
我为什么要帮你？

331
00:20:19,410 --> 00:20:23,540
-The reason he just said. -What do you need?
理由他已经说了 帮你什么？

333
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:28,080
I saw you on stage talking to that beautiful woman.
我看到你跟那个美女说话 

334
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:31,660
You know,Sarah. I wish I could talk to her.
就是莎拉  我很想跟她说话 

336
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:34,050
-Are you in love with her? -Yeah.
你爱上她了吗？ 对

337
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:37,160
Her. All of them. Anyone.
她，所有的女人 谁都好

338
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:40,330
Yeah. I've been there, my friend.
我是过来人

339
00:20:40,570 --> 00:20:43,200
Listen,I guarantee you keep your job...
我保证让你留下来

340
