348
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:12,920
Ross did learn something from each marriage.
其实罗斯每次结婚 都学到一点东西

349
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:15,430
How to make the next one even shorter?
学到如何让婚姻变短吗？

350
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,300
Wait a minute. That's not fair.
等等，这么说不公平

351
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:20,600
He was married to me a hell of a lot longer than he was to Emily.
我们的婚姻比他和艾蜜莉的长 

352
00:21:20,810 --> 00:21:23,670
He just didn't tell me.
他只是没告诉我

